To enable Apple Pay on www.slytrans.com:

1. Log in to your Stripe Dashboard (https://dashboard.stripe.com).
2. Go to Settings → Payment methods → Apple Pay.
3. Click "Add a new domain" and enter:
      www.slytrans.com
      slytrans.com
4. Stripe will show a "Download domain association file" button.
5. Download that file (it has no extension).
6. In this repository, REPLACE the entire content of this file
   (.well-known/apple-developer-merchantid-domain-association)
   with the downloaded file content and commit the change.
7. After deploying, visit:
      https://www.slytrans.com/.well-known/apple-developer-merchantid-domain-association
   You should see the file content (not this placeholder text).
8. Go back to the Stripe Dashboard and click "Verify domain" to complete setup.

Apple Pay will appear in the Stripe Payment Element automatically for customers
using Safari on iOS or macOS once the domain is verified.
